             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HPE has made the following patch kits available to resolve the
vulnerabilities with the OpenVMS TCPIP Bind Services and OpenVMS TCPIP IPC
Services for OpenVMS

| Platform              | Patch Kit Name                        |
|-----------------------|---------------------------------------|
| Alpha OpenVMS  V8.4	| DEC-AXPVMS-TCPIP_CVE_PAT-V0507-ECO5-4 |
| ITANIUM OpenVMS V8.4	| HP-I64VMS-TCPIP_CVE_PAT-V0507-ECO5-4  |

**Notes:**

  - For CVE-2008-0122, please contact HPE OpenVMS support to request patch
kit TCPIP$IPC_SHR (V5.7-ECO5B) that is now available after the above patch
release.
  - Please read the release notes of these kits for more information
including other features that are provided.

